sequenceDiagram
    participant PTY as PTY Manager<br/>(Tokio Read Loop)
    participant Shell as Shell Process
    participant Block as Block Manager
    participant DB as SQLite<br/>(StoragePort)
    participant AI as AI Subsystem
    participant IPC as Tauri Events
    participant UI as React Frontend

    Note over PTY,Shell: PTY read loop encounters failure

    alt I/O Error
        PTY->>PTY: read() returns error
    else Process Crash
        Shell->>PTY: EOF + non-zero signal
    end

    PTY->>Shell: Attempt kill(pid, SIGTERM)
    PTY->>Block: Finalize incomplete blocks<br/>with error state
    PTY->>DB: Flush command history
    PTY->>AI: Cancel pending AI requests<br/>for this session
    PTY->>PTY: Drop PTY file descriptors<br/>and Tokio task resources

    PTY->>IPC: emit pty:error(session_id,<br/>error_type, message)
    IPC->>UI: Receive pty:error event
    UI->>UI: Render ErrorBanner<br/>"Session failed: {message}"

    Note over UI: User sees two options

    alt User clicks "Close"
        UI->>UI: Remove terminal tab
    else User clicks "Reopen"
        UI->>IPC: invoke create_terminal_session()
        Note over UI: New session in same tab
    end
